    • REMOVE_ADMIN_ROLE_HEADER

      public static final String REMOVE_ADMIN_ROLE_HEADER
      Header to indicate that the request should remove admin role from the principal to test non-admin access. This is different from NOT_ADMIN_HEADER in that it is used to remove the admin role regardless of whether the request is from localhost or not.
